title: Borussia Dortmund 2-3 Bayer Leverkusen: Schick double hands hosts first home defeat
description: Two goals from Patrik Schick helped Bayer Leverkusen battle past Borussia Dortmund to a 3-2 victory on Friday, claiming a sixth-straight league win. Dortmund suffered their first home loss of the Bundesliga campaign, while Leverkusen moved within one point of leaders Bayern Munich. title: Miedema in line for Man City return after knee injury
description: Vivianne Miedema could make her return to the Manchester City squad for their FA Cup fourth-round tie on Sunday after a three-month injury absence.
